author: danj
msg: Fix for MUSE-57, as outlined in the submission. Updated AbstractFilePersistence abstract method to receive
the context path of the resource it was currently creating, allowing concrete classes such as RouterFilePersistence
to use this in the construction of EPRs. The WSN and WSSG persistence classes were updated to match the
method signature but otherwise had no code changes.
